{"tid":1423121,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"『街坊disco』和理非五大訴求廣場舞上線啦！","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:04:44.000Z","uid":170389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2aef7ae8f55bdd23a9185fb3ce837f653b24b290","tid":1423121,"uid":170389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:56:13.000Z","msg":"6月16日香港有200萬人connect<br />\n我希望connect 埋淨低既港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、師奶、甚至係小學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以要用琅琅上口既廣場舞等佢地背熟五大訴求 而且有人話訴求變質 咁我地更加要重申一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n靈感來自黃大仙跳舞既街坊同埋小人國既卸膊操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未睇過卸膊操既傳送門<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=_3KiZEXPGU4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_3KiZEXPGU4&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2BvwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=01f83ef8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=_3KiZEXPGU4</a><br />\n<br />\n拍子好簡單 前半一拍 後面半拍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(各位街坊 我地唔係黎示威 亦唔係黎集會 只係一齊跳廣場舞）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非-廣場舞 有五~大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非-廣場舞 有五~大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非-廣場舞 有五~大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(有邊五大訴求呀？)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全面撤回 逃犯~條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全面撤回 逃犯~條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全面撤回 逃犯~條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(除左撤回逃犯條例呢)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撤銷所有 暴動~定性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撤銷所有 暴動~定性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撤銷所有 暴動~定性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(沒有暴動 咁有無犯法)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n釋放義士 永不~追究<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n釋放義士 永不~追究<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n釋放義士 永不~追究<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(點解會有咁多衝突)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立即成立 獨立~調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立即成立 獨立~調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立即成立 獨立~調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(要調查乜野呀)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元朗暴力 官警~鄉黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元朗暴力 官警~鄉黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元朗暴力 官警~鄉黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(如果想香港變好要點做)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行會立會 我要~雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行會立會 我要~雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行會立會 我要~雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n街坊disco  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />深水埗見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣場舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廣場舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廣場舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家